    <selectionEntry id="23e5-ccc1-ea59-2953" name="The Betrayer O&apos;Kuro&apos;shi" hidden="false" collective="false" import="true" type="unit">
      <constraints>
        <constraint field="selections" scope="parent" value="1.0" percentValue="false" shared="true" includeChildSelections="false" includeChildForces="false" id="c9ab-3985-48d6-db23" type="max"/>
      </constraints>
      <rules>
        <rule id="6a7e-d483-983f-19c8" name="Ruinous Pressence" hidden="false">
          <description>With his battlesuit decorated with symbols of chaos, and an aura of warp power surrounding him, O’Kuro’shi is truly a fearsome pressence on the battlefield. All non-daemon models on the table, including your own, suffer a -1 modifier to their leadership value.</description>
        </rule>
        <rule id="e4c9-2ea9-605b-f646" name="Impervious" hidden="false">
          <description>Due to the amount of warp power constantly flowing around him, O’Kuro’shi is resilient against both physical and warp based attacks. Any psykers wishing to use a psychic power against O’Kuro’shi rolls an extra D6 and picks the two highest rolls when taking a Psychic Test. O&apos;Kuro&apos;shi is also immune to weapons that would cause instant death or cause more than one wound, only taking a single wound instead.</description>
        </rule>
        <rule id="c9b7-42e0-ef60-eee6" name="Daemonic Mutations" hidden="false">
          <description>Mutated by the ruinous powers of chaos O&apos;Kuro&apos;shi has gained a multitude of new powers, they manifest as follwing:
- Daemonic Armour (Included in profile)
- Daemonic Reslience (Included in profile)
- Daemonic Strength (Included in profile)
- Fleet Special Rule
- Furious Charge Special Rule
O&apos;Kuro&apos;shi also counts as a Daemon for the purpose of rules affecting daemons.</description>
        </rule>
        <rule id="f6b2-76d4-a68a-8a45" name="Warped Ammunition:" hidden="false">
          <description>With the powers of the warp constantly flowing around him, O’Kuro’shi&apos;s weapons become unstable  with daemonic energies 
At the start of the shooting phase you must roll a D6 and then consult the following table:
1: Overheat! The weapon overheats from the raw power of the warp, O’Kuro’shi suffers one wound (No saves allowed) and may not fire at all this turn.
2: Lasting Energies: Double the range of all weapons (Rapid Fire weapons fire twice at 24” instead of 12”)
3-4: Normal: All weapons follow their normal rules.
5: Piercing Power: All weapons count as AP1 and have double their strength (Up to a maximum of 10).
6: Overload! The weapon are overloaded from the raw power of the warp, O’kuro’shi suffers one wound (No saves allowed) but may fire as normal, using the result of 2 &amp; 5 together, in additon the weapons gains the blast rule.</description>
        </rule>
      </rules>
      <infoLinks>
        <infoLink id="b45a-8989-fe06-20fa" name="Shas&apos;o Kuro&apos;shi" hidden="false" targetId="9a66-ed76-622e-4940" type="profile"/>
        <infoLink id="3fc3-f1f3-9f1c-b039" name="Ion Rifle (burst)" hidden="false" targetId="7588-d987-bde1-5430" type="profile"/>
